EN: The impermanence of life makes us understand its meaning better.

ZH: 无常是生命中最可靠的朋友。
EN: Impermanence is the most reliable friend in life.

ZH: 面对无常，我们要学会适应变化。
EN: In the face of impermanence, we must learn to adapt to change.

ZH: 无常使人们更加懂得宽容。
EN: Impermanence makes people more understanding and tolerant.

ZH: 懂得无常让我更加珍惜人与人之间的真挚情感。
EN: Understanding impermanence makes me appreciate genuine emotions between people even more.

ZH: 在无常面前，唯一不变的是变化本身。
